#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layers.rst:18
msgid "Fill Layers"
msgstr "填充圖層"

#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layers.rst:20
msgid ""
"A Fill Layer is a special layer that Krita generates on-the-fly that can "
"contain either a pattern or a solid color."
msgstr "填充圖層是 Krita 動態生成來填滿整個畫布的特殊圖層，其中可以生成圖案或純色。"

#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/fill_layers.rst:25
msgid ""
"By default, the dialog selects the flat color fill. This fills the layer "
"with a singular color. Newly created colored fill layers will be assigned to "
"the currently active foreground color, unless they were made by drag-and-"
"dropping a :ref:`palette swatch <palette_docker>` onto the :ref:`layer stack "
"<layer_docker>`."
msgstr ""
"一班預設的情況下，新增填充圖層的對話視窗會是在「色彩」這個項目。會用單一的顏色填滿整個圖層。而新建時這個顏色會是目前的前景色，除非直接將 :ref:`"
"調色板 <調色板>`中的色票直接拖曳到 :ref:`圖層 <圖層>`面板中。"

